 video game area, internet facilities and a laundry area where you can wash, dry and iron. There is also a varied entertainment programme for everyone including a kids club, games such as football and volleyball, evening shows to entertain after dark and the weekly barbecue party by the pool , perfect for your holidays to Majorca.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>SurroundingArea</Type><Text>Jutlandia sits in a quiet but central location in the popular resort of Santa Ponsa on the island of Majorca. The beach, shops, bars and restaurants of Santa Ponsa are only 400 metres from the Jutlandia Apartments. Santa Ponsa is located on the south west coast of the island and is the ideal choice for a fun-packed holiday in the sun.</Text></Description><Amenity><Code>Safe</Code><Text>Safe</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>AirConditioning</Code><Text>Air conditioning</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Bar</Code><Text>Bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>LaundryService</Code><Text>Laundry service</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>CarPark</Code><Text>Car parking</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Garage</Code><Text>Garage</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>FreshWaterPool</Code><Text>Fresh Water Pool</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>SunBathingTerrace</Code><Text>Sun Bathing Terrace</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Balcony</Code><Text>Balcony</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>TelephoneInRoom</Code><Text>Direct Dial Telephone</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>BathRoom</Code><Text>Bath Room</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Heating</Code><Text>Heating</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Restaurants</Code><Text>Restaurants</Text></Amenity><Rating><System>Stars</System><Score>30</Score><Description>Three star</Description></Rating><Rank>1</Rank></HotelElement>